OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776089466
OL,3,CMan, 20, who suffered severe brain
OL,4,Cinjury in Ibiza defies all medical odds
OL,6,FThe parents of a man from Hampshire
OL,7,Fwho suffered a severe brain injury on
OL,8,Fa football holiday are urging young
OL,9,Fpeople who travel abroad to never walk
OL,10,Falone at night.
OL,12,FDan Hurst, from Yateley, had to
OL,13,Frebuild his life after an incident in
OL,14,FIbiza.
OL,16,FHe went on an annual football trip to
OL,17,Fthe popular holiday destination in May
OL,18,Flast year with his teammates from
OL,19,FYateley United Football Club.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
