PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776089466
OL,3,CMan, 20, who suffered severe brain
OL,4,Cinjury in Ibiza defies all medical odds
OL,6,FHe was found on the road and taken to
OL,7,Fhospital.
OL,9,FHe had suffered such a horrific head
OL,10,Finjury, medics didn't think he'd
OL,11,Fsurvive.
OL,13,FDan said: "I had some money and stuff
OL,14,Fand then that was gone. My wallet and
OL,15,FI think even my shoes were found but
OL,16,Fnot on me, so it's strange."
OL,18,FAfter nearly a year of investigating
OL,19,Fhis family are no closer to any
OL,20,Fanswers.
