PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776089466
OL,3,CMan, 20, who suffered severe brain
OL,4,Cinjury in Ibiza defies all medical odds
OL,6,FHis mum Mandy said: "It was the middle
OL,7,Fof the night, about 12:30 or 01:00.
OL,8,FIt's a phone call that no parent hopes
OL,9,Fthey'll ever get.
OL,11,F"Steve, his dad, saying that he'd been
OL,12,Finjured and at that point, he told me
OL,13,Fthat they didn't think he was going to
OL,14,Fmake it."
OL,16,FAfter four weeks in a coma in hospital
OL,17,Fin Spain, he was airlifted to Frimley
OL,18,FPark Hospital in Surrey.
OL,26,@vD@IO]
