PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776089466
OL,3,CMan, 20, who suffered severe brain
OL,4,Cinjury in Ibiza defies all medical odds
OL,6,FHe spent four months on a stroke unit
OL,7,Fin a bed for patients who suffer
OL,8,Ftraumatic brain injuries.
OL,10,FWhen he arrived at the hospital he was
OL,11,Funable to walk or talk but thanks to
OL,12,Fthe care he received he is now
OL,13,Fplanning to run the London Marathon
OL,15,FHe wants to raise awareness that
OL,16,F'recovery is possible' after such a
OL,17,Ftraumatic injury.
OL,19,FLater this month, Dan is running the
OL,20,FLondon marathon for those who helped
OL,21,Fhim at Frimley Health Charity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
