PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776089466
OL,3,CMan, 20, who suffered severe brain
OL,4,Cinjury in Ibiza defies all medical odds
OL,6,FHe said: "By doing the London Marathon
OL,7,F11 months after being in a coma, I am
OL,8,Fshowing other people and trying to
OL,9,Fhelp them know that recovery is always
OL,10,Fpossible."
